      "span_text": "Saccharomyces cerevisiae 6EA1 (leu2-3,112, trp1-1, ura3-1, can1-100, RPL12A::KanMX4, RPL12B::HIS3) originally called A6K1O-6EA1, was derived from strain W303 as previously described  ."
